ElementDescription: The NDAR Global Unique Identifier (GUID) for research subject
Subject ID how it's defined in lab/project
Age in months at the time of the interview/test/sampling/imaging.
Notes: Age is rounded to chronological month. If the research participant is 15-days-old at time of interview, the appropriate value would be 0 months. If the participant is 16-days-old, the value would be 1 month.

ElementDescription: Date on which the interview/genetic test/sampling/imaging/biospecimen was completed. MM/DD/YYYY

Notes: M = Male; F = Female; O=Other; NR = Not reported

ElementDescription: The event name for which the data was collected
In your opinion, compared to other boys/girls your age, how much physical activity do you do?
Notes: 1 = Much less; 2 = A little less; 3 = About the same; 4 = A little more; 5 = Much more

ElementDescription: In your opinion, compared to other boys/girls your age, how much sedentary behaviors do you do?
Notes: 1 = Much less; 2 = A little less; 3 = About the same; 4 = A little more; 5 = Much more

ElementDescription: In your opinion, compared to other boys/girls your age, how much sleep do you get?
Notes: 1 = Much less; 2 = A little less; 3 = About the same; 4 = A little more; 5 = Much more

ElementDescription: How often did you have to remove the Fitbit?
Notes: 1 = once per day; 2 = twice per day; 3 = 3-4 times per day; 4 = more than 4 times per day

ElementDescription: When did you take it off (during what activities)? (Can choose more than one) (1, Shower/Bath)
When did you take it off (during what activities)? (Can choose more than one) (2, Sports)
When did you take it off (during what activities)? (Can choose more than one) (3, Swimming)
When did you take it off (during what activities)? (Can choose more than one) (4, Sleep)
When did you take it off (during what activities)? (Can choose more than one) (5, Other)
How often did you check the Fitbit to get information about your activity?
Notes: 1 = Several times per day; 2 = About once per day; 3 = Several times per week; 4 = About once per week

ElementDescription: How much did you change your physical activity while wearing the Fitbit?
Notes: 1 = A lot; 2 = Not at all; 3 = A little

ElementDescription: How much did you change your sleep while wearing the Fitbit?
Notes: 1 = A lot; 2 = Not at all; 3 = A little

ElementDescription: Did you change your level of physical activity or amount of sleep based on the recorded activity on the app or website?
